Author: Christian Engels [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6198-431X>)
Maintainer: Christian Engels <ce50@st-andrews.ac.uk>
Description: Provides an interface for browsing, searching, and replying to Microsoft
    Outlook 365 emails with AI assistance. Allows users to use context-aware AI models
    to draft and refine email responses. Integrates with Microsoft Graph API and
    supports Anthropic Claude models.
